title: This cosplayer might be the most convincing Taylor Swift lookalike yet
text:
Meet the woman who looks so much like Taylor Swift, you'll want to ask her who she voted for .
The internet loves a good doppelg√§nger , and it's found one in April Gloria, a cosplayer who's nailed Taylor Swift's cat-eyed, red lipsticked signature look.
SEE ALSO: Ariana Grande lookalike has certainly mastered the high ponytail
Yes, friends, it's true: this is not actually Taylor Swift.
A photo posted by April (@april_gloria) on Feb 9, 2017 at 1:41pm PST
And the resemblance doesn't stop with appearance. April even has a cat named Milo, who definitely looks like he could be friends with Meredith and Olivia.
Perhaps they could throw a Fourth of July party together and invite all their cat friends who are also models.
A photo posted by April (@april_gloria) on Dec 6, 2016 at 6:47am PST
Just a suggestion.
